<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="Marley">
  <data key="d0">Marley</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Marley is Scrooge's deceased partner, whose death serves as a pivotal point in the story, emphasizing Scrooge's character traits.&lt;SEP&gt;Marley is a deceased character whose face haunts Scrooge, representing a reminder of the past and causing Scrooge emotional turmoil.&lt;SEP&gt;Marley is Scrooge's deceased partner, whose face appears to Scrooge in a moment of supernatural vision.</data>
