  <data key="d0">Old Joe</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Old Joe is a grey-haired man nearly seventy years old, who deals in wares and hosts individuals in his shop.&lt;SEP&gt;Old Joe is a character who reflects on his weaknesses and interactions with other characters over a bundle of belongings.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a2a8f6ce9730d70a780729ca8e92d0a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5954df0f689419ebdd8a0008ca543c1</data>
