<node id="The Woman">
  <data key="d0">The Woman</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">The Woman is an unnamed character who enters the shop first, carrying a heavy bundle, and engages in outspoken dialogue.&lt;SEP&gt;The Woman is a character who engages in dialogue with Old Joe about the belongings and expresses pragmatism in her actions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-a2a8f6ce9730d70a780729ca8e92d0a1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5954df0f689419ebdd8a0008ca543c1</data>
