  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Bundle refers to the load carried by the characters into the Shop, containing various items they wish to have assessed.&lt;SEP&gt;The Bundle refers to a collection of belongings, including items like bed-curtains and clothing, being discussed by the characters.</data>
