  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Belinda Cratchit is one of Bob Cratchit's daughters, representing the joys and struggles of the Cratchit family.&lt;SEP&gt;Belinda Cratchit is one of Bob Cratchit's daughters, depicted as assisting her mother in preparing for the family meal.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1932e9b8ed52abe1ef474137263a18e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9856cf623e8bc291b045f847afe980d4</data>
