  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Peter Cratchit is Bob Cratchit's son, who is seen participating in family activities and displaying a sense of pride in his appearance.&lt;SEP&gt;Peter Cratchit is one of the sons in the Cratchit Family, who shows concern for his father's well-being.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1932e9b8ed52abe1ef474137263a18e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e38b901b0e466ddad5ceba76c831be45</data>
