<node id="Martha">
  <data key="d0">Martha</data>
  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Martha is another daughter of Bob Cratchit, characterized by her late arrival and interaction with her family.&lt;SEP&gt;Martha is a character who hides from her father and later reveals herself during the Christmas gathering.&lt;SEP&gt;Martha is a family member working as an apprentice at a milliner's, who shares her work experiences with the family.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1932e9b8ed52abe1ef474137263a18e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-392109aa88dfa4908b740d7d5ae9eb90&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-66426a62a0a36fa251cf1d299186a70b</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
