</node>
<node id="Ghost of Christmas Present">
  <data key="d0">Ghost of Christmas Present</data>
  <data key="d1">creature</data>
  <data key="d2">The Ghost of Christmas Present is a spirit that reveals the current state of joy and generosity during Christmas.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ghost of Christmas Present is a spirit that appears to Scrooge, embodying joy and abundance, and guiding him to learn valuable lessons.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ghost of Christmas Present is a spirit that represents generosity and brings joy, guiding Scrooge through scenes of family life and societal responsibility.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ghost of Christmas Present is a mystical being that participates in the festivities and reveals insights into Scrooge's character and interactions during Christmas.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ghost of Christmas Present symbolizes generosity and the joy of the current season, showing Scrooge the importance of living in the moment.&lt;SEP&gt;The Ghost of Christmas Present is a character that influences Scrooge's transformation and holiday spirit.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-1932e9b8ed52abe1ef474137263a18e4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fd81f881ed78bcf87091e0e941d68113&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0bc83756fd962e6c68b4dbd7edab915&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-51d7a4cb6ae0bc446d77d68d64376739&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9856cf623e8bc291b045f847afe980d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f077bd292c07915b352ff9fce2ec4a53</data>
