  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Mr. Marley was Scrooge's former partner who has been deceased for seven years; his legacy and liberality are mentioned by two gentlemen.&lt;SEP&gt;Mr. Marley is a deceased character, mentioned as having died seven years ago, who had a notable partnership with Scrooge.</data>
